prompts.frontCover: Vivid greeting card front cover, dreamy fantasy art style, flat 2D illustration. A romantic anniversary scene on a tranquil beach at sunset. A cartoon-style man and woman are sitting together on a large, intricately patterned bohemian blanket spread on the soft sand. They are leaning against each other affectionately, smiling warmly as they sip from unique boba teas served in hollowed-out coconut shells with bamboo straws. The sky is a breathtaking gradient of pastel pink, soft lavender, and warm orange, with gentle, ethereal clouds swirling like cotton candy. The setting sun casts a magical golden glow over the scene. The ocean waves are calm and mystical, sparkling with bioluminescent plankton that twinkles like submerged stars. Whimsical elements float gently in the air: glowing jellyfish-like orbs and tiny, sparkling fairy lights. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Anniversary, my love". The overall atmosphere is serene, magical, and deeply romantic.
